objective:
本課程主要教授學生七大項方向:
1.複習矩陣學
2.結構矩陣學基本概念
3.勁度法觀念
4.勁度法解桁架問題
5.勁度法解梁問題
6.勁度法解剛架問題
7.程式分析實習

學生需具有矩陣分析、材料力學與結構學之基本知識。

===============
The course contents are divided into 7 major topics:
1. Review the matrix theory; 
2.Basic concepts of the matrix structural theory; 
3. Stiffness method; 
4. Using stiffness method to solve truss problem; 
5. Using stiffness method to solve beam problem; 
6. Using stiffness method to solve rigid frame problem; 
7. Practice of the structural analysis program.

Students must have the knowledge of  Matrix Analysis, Mechanics of Materials, and Theory of Structures.

materials:
教材以老師的講義為主。

參考書籍:
Sack, R.L., “Matrix Structural Analysis”, 1994; 
Kassimali, A.,  “Matrix Analysis of Structures”, 2nd Ed.; 
Mcguire, Gallagher, Ziemain, “Matrix Structural Analysis”, 2000.
